        <briefdescription>
<para>Begin a firmware update. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Erases the first sector of the target slot and prepares for writing. The image header is written at slot_addr; image data starts at slot_addr + sizeof(SYN_FwImageHeader).</para>
